name.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Mitbbs and Huaren Youtube Auto Post

short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This extension automatically converts youtube links to the embeded format supported on the huaren.us and mitbbs.com forum

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
MITBBS Youtube link automatic converter.

It will convert youtube links from its original format to the embed format accepted by mitbbs.

Example:
Original format: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=peiiLCCG_Ng
will be converted to mitbbs format: vhttp://www.youtube.com/v/peiiLCCG_Ng
